SUMMARY:Modernizing .NET at Scale with the GitHub Copilot App Mod Agent
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nLearn how the GitHub Copilot App Mo
 dernization Agent brings agentic automation to .NET modernization. We’ll
  walk through assessing apps at scale through the CLI\, generating moderni
 zation plans\, and executing upgrades in IDE workflows—accelerating the 
 path to Azure-ready apps.\n\n📌 This session is a part of a series! [Lea
 rn more here](https://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-1625/?wt.mc
 _id=meetup_S-1625_webpage_reactor)
